<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.4.1/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-HSMxcRTRxnN+Bdg0JdbxYKrThecOKuH5zCYotlSAcp1+c8xmyTe9GYg1l9a69psu" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/landing.css">

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.4.1/css/bootstrap.min.css"/>
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.5.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.4.1/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
    
    <title>What do you meme?</title>
</head>
<body>
    
<div class="create-join-room">
    <p class="help">
        <button
          class="btn btn-primary"
          type="button"
          data-toggle="collapse"
          data-target="#collapseExample"
          aria-expanded="false"
          aria-controls="collapseExample"
        >
          Help
        </button>
      </p>
      <div class="collapse" id="collapseExample">
        <div class="card-body-header"><h3>How to play?</h3></div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <ol>
              <li>Create and share room-code with your friends.</li>
              <li>All players are given random meme cards and a common scenario shows up.</li>
              <li>Pick the most relatable meme for the given scenario according to you. </li>
              <li>Submit and wait for everyone to pick.</li>
              <li>Upvote the funniest meme for the scenario, you cannot vote for yourself.</li>
              <li>The player with most votes get points.</li>
              <li>After all players voted, you will see the winning meme and scenario.</li>
              <li>Laugh with everyone and wait for 10 secs for the next round to begin.</li>
              <li>After all rounds, the player with most points is crowned the best memer.</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
      </div>

    <div class="create-join-room-header">
        Come on, let's play!
    </div>
    <div class="create-join-room-options">
        <div class="create-room">
            <!-- <div class="create-room-img">
                <img src={createBg} />
            </div> -->
            <div class="create-room-header">
                CREATE A ROOM
            </div>
            <div class="create-room-button">
                <button>CREATE</button>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="join-room">
            <!-- <div class="join-room-img">
                <img src={joinBg} />
            </div> -->
            <div class="join-room-header">
                JOIN A ROOM
            </div>
            <div class="join-room-button">
                <button>JOIN</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<%- include('partials/footer') -%>
